headline: These 3 Zacks 'Strong Buy' Stocks Reflect the Hottest S&P 500 Stocks of 2026
summary: Shares of these three red-hot companies continue to remain at the top of the S&P 500 leaderboard, underpinned by all being Zacks Rank #1 (Strong Buy) stocks. Coincidence? Not so much.
